Former Starboy music act L.A.X who is now signed to Rasaki Music Group is gearing for the release of his sophomore album, “Rasaking” but he has decided to tease fans with new music while they anticipate the soon to be released album. The music star who has been hailed as one of the industry’s most innovative artists will be releasing “Rasaking” under Rasaki Music Group on October 26th, 2018. Ahead of that, he has teased with a new song titled “Bad”, off the album, and he features the energetic “Mama Africa” crooner Yemi Alade on the track. The song was produced by Spotless. Listen to the teaser HERE.